{"title":"闹剧收场（图片）","authors":["池北偶朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹剧收场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗朱根华画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所谓“世纪之审”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是丑事一桩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耗资四千多万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹得沸沸扬扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两帮政客较劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双方舌剑唇枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各有一套说辞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大致旗鼓相当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这方把柄在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓住辫子不放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽把总统搞臭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无奈弹劾泡汤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那方竭力招架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反驳慷慨激昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保住白宫宝座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但也脸上无光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明党派争斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对话冠冕堂皇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折腾没完没了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招来倒彩满堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管怨声载道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧吵吵嚷嚷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好戏已难再唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹剧只好收场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国议会民主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟是这般模样。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}